Package project.controllers.repository

Interface I_UniqueQueryableRepository<T,​R extends I_RepositoryItem & I_Unique<T>>

Type Parameters:
T - the type of the queryable unique the object the repository stores has.
R - the type of object the repository stores.
All Known Implementing Classes:
DrugRepositoryController, UserRepositoryController
public interface I_UniqueQueryableRepository<T,​R extends I_RepositoryItem & I_Unique<T>>
Defines the functions of a repository controller which can be queried by a string. These functions only work if the queried objects have uniquely identifiable strings.
